title: Harvesting head with bark stripping
summary: A harvesting head with bark stripping, able to fell, de-limb and cut timber to required lengths

eligible.eligibleBullet01: be a harvesting head with bark stripping
eligible.eligibleBullet02: be able to fell and de-limb
eligible.eligibleBullet03: be able to cut timber to required lengths
eligible.eligibleBullet04: shear cut trees of at least 300mm in diameter
eligible.eligibleBullet05: remove all the bark from the trunk during delimbing
eligible.eligibleBullet06: fell and cut trees of minimum 150mm in diameter
eligible.eligibleBullet07: have a feed speed of at least 2m per second
